metadata.name: Vampiress
metadata.description:
The first piece of the collection is Vampiress. It is a very important artwork for me. She starts this collection and she worth it. This is a reflection of my vision of beauty, mystery, sensuality, and a reminder that beauty can be dangerous. 

Can you feel the scent of the night? Congratulations, you are charmed.


• Drawn from scratch in Photoshop ( 3384x5307px )

• You'll receive two versions of high-resolution images for printing.
